OL,3,CCharities urge quick government action
OL,4,Cover 'bleak' homelessness report
OL,6,FJersey's situation is "no better than
OL,7,Fa year ago" and the "outlook remains
OL,8,Fbleak", a new report has concluded.
OL,10,FThe area's Strategic Board, made up of
OL,11,Flocal community groups, says that 406
OL,12,Fpeople asked for shelter from five
OL,13,Fcharities in 2023.
OL,15,FThe most common reasons for
OL,16,Fhomelessness were reported as domestic
OL,17,Fviolence, relationship breakdowns,
OL,18,Fbeing in unsafe or insecure housing,
OL,19,Fand eviction.
