OL,3,CCharities urge quick government action
OL,4,Cover 'bleak' homelessness report
OL,6,FFour years ago, the Board released its
OL,7,F2020 Homelessness Strategy that called
OL,8,Fon Jersey's Government to clarify its
OL,9,Fofficial definition of homelessness
OL,10,Fand then collect data against it.
OL,12,FIn October 2022, former Housing and
OL,13,FCommunities Minister Deputy David Warr
OL,14,Fsaid that the Government would publish
OL,15,Fhomelessness statistics in March 2023.
OL,17,FHowever, this data is yet to be
OL,18,Freleased.
