OL,3,CCharities urge quick government action
OL,4,Cover 'bleak' homelessness report
OL,6,FThe Board's Chair, Simon Burgess,
OL,7,Fstated: "Without collating this
OL,8,Finformation, the Government will only
OL,9,Fbe second-guessing as to the steps
OL,10,Fneeded to tackle the issues.
OL,12,F"This will prevent the homelessness
OL,13,Fstrategy from being implemented in
OL,14,Ffull."
OL,16,FIn January 2024, the newly appointed
OL,17,FHousing Minister, Deputy Sam Mezec,
OL,18,Fsaid he was committed to implementing
OL,19,Fall of the recommendations of the
OL,20,Fhomelessness strategy - something the
OL,21,Fsector says is urgently needed.
